@startuml
autonumber
actor "User" as User

participant "Frontend (React)" as Frontend
participant "Web API (Controllers)" as API
participant "Business Logic (Services)" as Services
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

User -> Frontend: Submits Login/Register form
Frontend -> API: POST /api/auth/login or /api/auth/register
API -> Services: Calls AuthService for login/registration
Services -> DB: Verifies credentials or creates new user
DB --> Services: Returns user data or success/failure
Services --> API: Returns JWT or registration result
API --> Frontend: Sends JWT or confirmation
Frontend --> User: Redirects to dashboard or shows error

@enduml
